It's not that easy.

996
00:47:36.514 --> 00:47:41.451
Life's not easy. son.
I'll tell you.

997
00:47:46.557 --> 00:47:49.030
I love my family.

998
00:47:50.264 --> 00:47:52.165
I do.

999
00:47:54.565 --> 00:47:57.709
(sighs):
I just want to do my own thing.

1000
00:47:57.733 --> 00:47:59.777
Joseph's never gonna change.

1001
00:47:59.801 --> 00:48:03.715
Only thing he cares about
is the Jackson family.

1002
00:48:03.739 --> 00:48:04.683
Huh?

1003
00:48:04.707 --> 00:48:05.992
And no matter what you do.

1004
00:48:06.016 --> 00:48:10.161
he's only ever gonna see it
as a family success.

1005
00:48:10.185 --> 00:48:12.559
Get your own team.

1006
00:48:12.583 --> 00:48:14.935
Get you a good lawyer.

1007
00:48:14.959 --> 00:48:16.695
Think about it.

1008
00:48:16.719 --> 00:48:20.424
("Ben" by The Jacksons playing)

1009
00:48:24.298 --> 00:48:28.212
♪ Ben.
the two of us need look ♪

1010
00:48:28.236 --> 00:48:31.743
-♪ No more ♪
-(cheering. screaming loudly)

1011
00:48:31.767 --> 00:48:35.681
♪ We both found what we were ♪

1012
00:48:35.705 --> 00:48:38.651
♪ Looking for ♪

1013
00:48:38.675 --> 00:48:43.821
♪ With a friend
to call my own ♪

1014
00:48:43.845 --> 00:48:47.528
♪ I'll never be alone ♪

1015
00:48:47.552 --> 00:48:51.598
♪ And you.
my friend. will see ♪

1016
00:48:51.622 --> 00:48:54.909
♪ You've got a friend in me ♪

1017
00:48:54.933 --> 00:48:57.769
(cheering. screaming continue)

1018
00:48:57.793 --> 00:49:00.409
♪♪

1019
00:49:00.433 --> 00:49:05.117
-♪ Ben. you're always running ♪
-(speaking indistinctly)

1020
00:49:05.141 --> 00:49:08.087
♪ Here and there ♪

1021
00:49:08.111 --> 00:49:12.685
♪ You feel you're not wanted ♪

1022
00:49:12.709 --> 00:49:15.754
♪ Anywhere ♪

1023
00:49:15.778 --> 00:49:20.825
♪ If you ever look behind ♪

1024
00:49:20.849 --> 00:49:24.136
♪ And don't like
what you find ♪

1025
00:49:24.160 --> 00:49:26.974
-♪ There's something ♪
-(cheering. screaming)

1026
00:49:26.998 --> 00:49:28.404
♪ You should know ♪

1027
00:49:28.428 --> 00:49:34.135
♪ You've got a place to go ♪

1028
00:49:38.801 --> 00:49:44.475
♪ Like Ben. ♪

1029
00:49:46.083 --> 00:49:47.456
