1031
00:49:51.451 --> 00:49:53.616
(elevator bell dings)

1032
00:49:57.523 --> 00:49:59.897
SENIOR PARTNER:
So. we appreciate you coming in

1033
00:49:59.921 --> 00:50:03.835
and we applaud your decision
to seek independent counsel.

1034
00:50:03.859 --> 00:50:06.772
We can assure you the most
comprehensive attention

1035
00:50:06.796 --> 00:50:08.180
