MAN:
Too much of one.

1040
00:50:19.149 --> 00:50:22.062
I mean. the whole point's
going solo. right?

1041
00:50:22.086 --> 00:50:23.789
So. that means
you're probably gonna

1042
00:50:23.813 --> 00:50:27.419
break a few hearts
over there in Encino.

1043
00:50:30.094 --> 00:50:33.194
Unless I'm missing something.

1044
00:50:39.235 --> 00:50:42.346
-Do I know you?
-MAN: No. I don't think so.

1045
00:50:42.370 --> 00:50:44.282
MICHAEL:
You sure?

1046
00:50:44.306 --> 00:50:47.417
Yeah. I think I'd remember.

1047
00:50:47.441 --> 00:50:49.485
Who are you?

1048
00:50:49.509 --> 00:50:52.004
John Branca.

1049
00:50:52.182 --> 00:50:55.227
-You handle The Beach Boys.
-BRANCA: Yeah. I do.

1050
00:50:55.251 --> 00:50:56.459
Neil Diamond. Bob Dylan.

1051
00:50:56.483 --> 00:50:59.946
couple other guys.
and now I work here.

1052
00:51:00.058 --> 00:51:01.827
I like The Beach Boys.

1053
00:51:01.851 --> 00:51:02.597
Me. too.

1054
00:51:02.621 --> 00:51:03.796
Brian Wilson's a genius.

1055
00:51:03.820 --> 00:51:07.360
Some of the best harmonies
in rock and roll.

1056
00:51:10.200 --> 00:51:12.640
You know what
I'm after. Mr. Branca?

1057
00:51:12.664 --> 00:51:14.246
BRANCA:
Sure.

1058
00:51:14.270 --> 00:51:17.601
You want to be
the biggest star in the world.

1059
00:51:20.705 --> 00:51:23.574
Can you help make that happen?

1060
00:51:24.082 --> 00:51:25.774
Yes.

1061
00:51:26.447 --> 00:51:28.018
How?

1062
00:51:28.042 --> 00:51:32.913
Because I believe
there's no one like you.

1063
00:51:33.256 --> 00:51:36.290
And there never will be.

1064
00:51:43.266 --> 00:51:45.959
SENIOR PARTNER:
Mr. Jackson...

1065
00:51:46.467 --> 00:51:47.345
Mr. Jackson.

1066
00:51:47.369 --> 00:51:50.601
-I apologize...
-He's my guy.

1067
00:51:53.705 --> 00:51:57.245
Can you leave us alone
for a second?

1068
00:51:57.511 --> 00:51:58.983
Please.

1069
00:51:59.007 --> 00:52:00.952
MAN 1:
Of course.

1070
00:52:00.976 --> 00:52:03.075
Yes.

1071
00:52:07.389 --> 00:52:10.126
(door opens)

1072
00:52:12.955 --> 00:52:14.273
(door closes)

1073
00:52:14.297 --> 00:52:15.868
Okay. Mr. Branca.

1074
00:52:15.892 --> 00:52:20.466
-(clears throat)
-Here's your first job.

1075
00:52:21.535 --> 00:52:24.800
