1081
00:52:36.979 --> 00:52:39.683
(plucking notes)

1082
00:52:39.949 --> 00:52:42.884
(machine beeps. whirs)

1083
00:53:02.213 --> 00:53:04.323
-Yes.
-I think it goes...

1084
00:53:04.347 --> 00:53:05.588
Button it up like this.

1085
00:53:05.612 --> 00:53:06.622
-Oh. right.
-Yeah.

1086
00:53:06.646 --> 00:53:10.043
La Toya. get the hell on
out of here.

1087
00:53:10.617 --> 00:53:12.661
Kate. look at this.

1088
00:53:12.685 --> 00:53:13.728
Will you look at this?

1089
00:53:13.752 --> 00:53:16.170
The boy fired me
with a piece of paper.

1090
00:53:16.194 --> 00:53:19.272
A piece of... Couldn't
even be man-to-man. huh?

1091
00:53:19.296 --> 00:53:21.373
Look me in the eye and do it.

1092
00:53:21.397 --> 00:53:24.695
That boy's gonna feel my belt
when he get in here!

1093
00:53:25.126 --> 00:53:27.104
No. he's not.

1094
00:53:27.128 --> 00:53:29.447
-Yes. the hell he is.
-No. he's not.

1095
00:53:29.471 --> 00:53:31.878
What are you gonna do. beat him?

1096
00:53:31.902 --> 00:53:34.518
You gonna whup him?

1097
00:53:34.542 --> 00:53:35.915
He's grown.

1098
00:53:35.939 --> 00:53:38.412
What'd you say to me?

1099
00:53:39.877 --> 00:53:43.395
I said you can't do it no more.

1100
00:53:43.419 --> 00:53:46.321
You can't whup nobody.

1101
00:53:46.950 --> 00:53:49.588
You can't beat nobody.

1102
00:53:50.052 --> 00:53:54.153
And if you don't like it.
you can leave.

1103
00:53:58.269 --> 00:54:00.214
And the next time
you see your son.

1104
00:54:00.238 --> 00:54:01.743
you ought to thank him.

1105
00:54:01.767 --> 00:54:03.778
Everything we have
is because of him

1106
00:54:03.802 --> 00:54:05.813
and don't you ever forget that.

1107
00:54:05.837 --> 00:54:07.045
Everybody seems to forget

1108
00:54:07.069 --> 00:54:11.137
that I'm the one
that got us out of Gary.

1109
00:54:12.074 --> 00:54:14.657
And everything I've done

1110
00:54:14.681 --> 00:54:16.494
is for this family.

1111
00:54:16.518 --> 00:54:20.784
You go on ahead
and keep thinking that.

1112
00:54:22.260 --> 00:54:25.624
(leaves rustling)

1113
00:54:27.397 --> 00:54:28.308
(giraffe grunts)

1114
00:54:28.332 --> 00:54:31.542
("Enjoy Yourself"
by The Jacksons playing)

1115
00:54:31.566 --> 00:54:33.940
<i>♪ Enjoy yourself.
enjoy yourself ♪</i>

1116
00:54:33.964 --> 00:54:35.942
<i>♪ Enjoy yourself with me ♪</i>

1117
00:54:35.966 --> 00:54:38.318
<i>♪ Enjoy yourself.
enjoy yourself ♪</i>

1118
00:54:38.342 --> 00:54:40.452
♪ Enjoy yourself with me ♪

1119
00:54:40.476 --> 00:54:44.104
♪ You better enjoy yourself ♪

1120
00:54:44.513 --> 00:54:46.986
-(loud pop)
-♪ You better enjoy yourself ♪

1121
00:54:47.010 --> 00:54:49.857
-(Michael laughing)
-(toy squeaks)

1122
00:54:49.881 --> 00:54:51.628
MICHAEL:
<i>You didn't go down this side.</i>

1123
00:54:51.652 --> 00:54:54.268
-Left.
-Where? This? Left? Going left. All right.

1124
00:54:54.292 --> 00:54:56.435
-(train whistle blows)
-♪ While people are dancin' ♪

1125
00:54:56.459 --> 00:54:59.196
-♪ Dancin' all over the place
♪ -BILL: A little choo choo train.

1126
00:54:59.220 --> 00:55:01.803
