1128
00:55:03.994 --> 00:55:06.841
♪ Come on. girl.
while the night is young... ♪

1129
00:55:06.865 --> 00:55:08.205
Yeah. So. I'm really excited.

1130
00:55:08.229 --> 00:55:09.613
-This looks really cool.
-(music stops)

1131
00:55:09.637 --> 00:55:10.779
MICHAEL:
That's you.

1132
00:55:10.803 --> 00:55:12.319
BOY: I can't wait
to start playing it.

1133
00:55:12.343 --> 00:55:13.386
That's Michael Jackson.

1134
00:55:13.410 --> 00:55:15.014
-What?
-It's Michael Jackson.

1135
00:55:15.038 --> 00:55:16.642
What?!

1136
00:55:16.842 --> 00:55:18.017
Please excuse him. (chuckles)

1137
00:55:18.041 --> 00:55:21.460
Are-Are you. um.
are you actually. really...

1138
00:55:21.484 --> 00:55:23.055
Yeah. I'm Michael. yeah.

1139
00:55:23.079 --> 00:55:25.222
-Wow.
-Mom. it's...

1140
00:55:25.246 --> 00:55:26.190
I wonder...

1141
00:55:26.214 --> 00:55:27.862
I'd love an autograph.

1142
00:55:27.886 --> 00:55:29.930
For my son. I mean. (chuckles)

1143
00:55:29.954 --> 00:55:32.570
-Honey?
