1159
00:56:02.855 --> 00:56:03.601
Hi.

1160
00:56:03.625 --> 00:56:05.966
-Would you like an autograph?
-Yes. please.

1161
00:56:05.990 --> 00:56:08.067
-What's your name?
-Anika.

1162
00:56:08.091 --> 00:56:09.409
Anika. That's a pretty name.

1163
00:56:09.433 --> 00:56:11.939
-MAN: What do you say. baby?
-ANIKA: Thank you.

1164
00:56:11.963 --> 00:56:13.941
WOMAN:
We're huge fans.

1165
00:56:13.965 --> 00:56:15.239
MICHAEL:
Thank you so much.

1166
00:56:15.263 --> 00:56:17.384
-<i>♪ Enjoy yourself ♪</i>
-♪ Let's get on down ♪

1167
00:56:17.408 --> 00:56:19.012
-<i>♪ Enjoy yourself ♪</i>
-Thanks.

1168
00:56:19.036 --> 00:56:21.421
MICHAEL:
Hey. everybody. Too cute.

1169
00:56:21.445 --> 00:56:23.753
-(music stops)
-(chattering)

1170
00:56:23.777 --> 00:56:24.754
Over here. over here.

1171
00:56:24.778 --> 00:56:27.845
