1182
00:56:45.634 --> 00:56:47.645
<i>-Twister?</i>
-You want to play tonight?

1183
00:56:47.669 --> 00:56:48.910
-Michael. <i>Twister?</i>
-Really?

1184
00:56:48.934 --> 00:56:50.241
What we gonna do
with <i>Twister.</i> man?

1185
00:56:50.265 --> 00:56:51.748
Come on.
It'll be like the old days.

1186
00:56:51.772 --> 00:56:53.211
Would love to. Mike.
but I got to be home

1187
00:56:53.235 --> 00:56:54.850
with the family.
I can't be playing games.

1188
00:56:54.874 --> 00:56:56.522
MARLON: And the rest of us
are going out tonight.

1189
00:56:56.546 --> 00:56:58.458
-TITO: Yeah. Marlon's got a hot date.
-MARLON: Yeah.

1190
00:56:58.482 --> 00:56:59.954
-(brothers laughing)
-Marlon. what time

1191
00:56:59.978 --> 00:57:01.692
are you gonna be home?
We could play then.

1192
00:57:01.716 --> 00:57:03.958
Hey. Marlon's gonna be playing
his own game of <i>Twister.</i>

1193
00:57:03.982 --> 00:57:05.498
-(brothers exclaim)
-MARLON: Shut up. Jackie.

1194
00:57:05.522 --> 00:57:07.665
-I'm always lucky.
-(brothers laugh)

1195
00:57:07.689 --> 00:57:09.095
JACKIE:
Yeah. right.

1196
00:57:09.119 --> 00:57:10.294
You guys are no fun anymore.

1197
00:57:10.318 --> 00:57:12.362
JERMAINE: Come on. Mike.
Don't be like that.

1198
00:57:12.386 --> 00:57:15.068
