no lovin'... ♪

1204
00:57:24.266 --> 00:57:26.112
It's okay.

1205
00:57:26.136 --> 00:57:27.817
Don't worry about it.

1206
00:57:27.841 --> 00:57:29.423
It takes a long time to learn

1207
00:57:29.447 --> 00:57:33.812
