-(chattering)

1208
00:57:34.012 --> 00:57:35.022
You want some ice cream?

1209
00:57:35.046 --> 00:57:36.727
♪ Don't blame it
on the sunshine... ♪

1210
00:57:36.751 --> 00:57:38.157
Okay. but then
I've got to go to work.

1211
00:57:38.181 --> 00:57:40.599
Don't break anything.

1212
00:57:40.623 --> 00:57:42.161
I'll be back.

1213
00:57:42.185 --> 00:57:42.898
(chattering)

1214
00:57:42.922 --> 00:57:44.537
♪ Don't blame it
on the sunshine ♪

1215
00:57:44.561 --> 00:57:47.034
♪ Don't blame it on the
moonlight ♪ -(hooting)

1216
00:57:47.058 --> 00:57:49.399
♪ Don't blame it
on the good times ♪

1217
00:57:49.423 --> 00:57:51.808
♪ Blame it on the boogie.
whoo... ♪

1218
00:57:51.832 --> 00:57:53.403
(Bubbles screeching)

1219
00:57:53.427 --> 00:57:55.548
♪♪

1220
00:57:55.572 --> 00:57:58.507
(Michael humming)

1221
00:58:00.170 --> 00:58:04.007
-(music stops abruptly)
-(Michael gasps softly)

1222
00:58:07.243 --> 00:58:10.585
I was thinking
about framing this.

1223
00:58:16.285 --> 00:58:17.955
Read it.

1224
00:58:19.123 --> 00:58:22.355
Go on. Read it.

1225
00:58:26.295 --> 00:58:28.878
Firing your own father.

1226
00:58:28.902 --> 00:58:31.804
What kind of son does that?

1227
00:58:36.778 --> 00:58:39.680
(sighs)
Michael...

1228
