You got a lot to learn
about family.

1229
00:58:53.696 --> 00:58:54.739
(door slams shut)

1230
00:58:54.763 --> 00:58:56.642
-("The Love You Save" playing)
-♪ Stop. na. na. na ♪

1231
00:58:56.666 --> 00:58:58.776
♪ You'd better save it ♪

1232
00:58:58.800 --> 00:59:03.374
♪ Stop. stop. stop.
you'd better save it ♪

1233
00:59:03.398 --> 00:59:05.046
♪ Whoo... ♪

1234
00:59:05.070 --> 00:59:07.312
(vocalizing)

1235
00:59:07.336 --> 00:59:09.556
-Hi. Welcome back. Michael.
-Hi.

1236
00:59:09.580 --> 00:59:11.558
MICHAEL:
Beautiful name.

1237
00:59:11.582 --> 00:59:12.757
PHOTOGRAPHER:
Look up for us.

1238
