all over their bodies.

2043
01:38:35.141 --> 01:38:37.614
It just breaks my heart.

2044
01:38:37.638 --> 01:38:40.078
It truly does.

2045
01:38:40.740 --> 01:38:43.873
You know. it got me thinking...

2046
